04-05 July - Baking Powder Cookies

5 cup flour
5 tablespoon baking powder
1 cup melted crisco
1/2 cup milk
1 cup sugar
6 eggs
2 teaspoon vanilla
1 tablespoon lemon juice

Mix crisco and milk together. Mix all ingredients and let stand for 15 minutes. Shape dough any way you want. Bake in a preheated 375F oven for about 8-10 minutes. The bottoms of cookies should brown, the top should be white. Cover with icing when cooled. 